{"blogid": "126370087", "writerAge": "码龄4年", "writerBlogNum": "987", "writerCollect": "5811", "writerComment": "454", "writerFan": "3855", "writerGrade": "7级", "writerIntegral": "16858", "writerName": "硬汉eric2013", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_126370087.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "611", "writerRankWeekly": "4351", "writerThumb": "1325", "writerVisitNum": "866295", "blog_read_count": "653", "blog_time": "于 2022-08-16 17:35:53 发布", "blog_title": "《安富莱嵌入式周报》第278期：基于RUST编程语言RTOS，固态继电器芯片，微软发布物联网组件框架，支持多款蜂窝，LoRa和WiFi芯片工业物联网4.0书籍", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p><strong>往期周报汇总地址：<strong><a href=\"http://www.armbbs.cn/forum.php?mod=forumdisplay&amp;fid=12&amp;filter=typeid&amp;typeid=104\" title=\"嵌入式周报 - uCOS &amp; uCGUI &amp; emWin &amp; embOS &amp; TouchGFX &amp; ThreadX -  硬汉嵌入式论坛 -  Powered by Discuz!\">嵌入式周报 - uCOS &amp; uCGUI &amp; emWin &amp; embOS &amp; TouchGFX &amp; ThreadX - 硬汉嵌入式论坛 - Powered by Discuz!</a></strong></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\051dcdf1c5c24427aed6d1694d072a3a.jpeg\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>本周更新一期视频教程</strong></p>\n<p>DSP视频教程第10期：DSP运算加速的精髓，含SIMD指令，饱和运算指令和浮点以及定点的MAC乘累加指令（2022-08-14）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.armbbs.cn/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=114725\" title=\"DSP视频教程第10期：DSP运算加速的精髓，含SIMD指令，饱和运算指令和浮点以及定点的MAC乘累加指令 - STM32H7 -  硬汉嵌入式论坛 -  Powered by Discuz!\">DSP视频教程第10期：DSP运算加速的精髓，含SIMD指令，饱和运算指令和浮点以及定点的MAC乘累加指令 - STM32H7 - 硬汉嵌入式论坛 - Powered by Discuz!</a></p>\n<p><br/><strong>视频版：</strong></p>\n<p><a class=\"link-info\" href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1y14y147Qt?zw\" title=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1y14y147Qt?zw\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1y14y147Qt?zw</a></p>\n<div class=\"csdn-video-box\">\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" data-mediaembed=\"bilibili\" id=\"vpliM8cr-1660640836704\" src=\"https://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=772081264\"></iframe>\n<p>《安富莱嵌入式周报》第278期：基于RUST编程语言RTOS，固态继电器芯片，微软发布物联网组件框架，支持多款蜂窝，LoRa和WiFi芯片工业物联网4.0书籍</p>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<p><br/><strong>1、ThreadX全家桶的嵌入式无线组件上线，当前支持LoRa，蜂窝和WiFi</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Azure/embedded-wireless-framework\" title=\"GitHub - Azure/embedded-wireless-framework: Microsoft's Embedded Wireless Framework is a design concept that enables users to abstract application code from host port drivers and communication adapter drivers primarily in microcontroller-based projects.\">GitHub - Azure/embedded-wireless-framework: Microsoft's Embedded Wireless Framework is a design concept that enables users to abstract application code from host port drivers and communication adapter drivers primarily in microcontroller-based projects.</a></p>\n<p>当前发布了首版，后面还将持续更新，支持更多的无线方式和相应器件的支持</p>\n<p>首版支持的器件</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\17d54838de1a4fbeb93b59db16e559be.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>框架</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\09c256b083a3401d838b7f1497113e0d.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>2、基于RUST编程语言的开源免费实时中断驱动系统RTIC，支持所有M内核芯片</strong></p>\n<p>文档:  <a href=\"https://rtic.rs/1/book/en/preface.html\" title=\"Preface - Real-Time Interrupt-driven Concurrency\">Preface - Real-Time Interrupt-driven Concurrency</a></p>\n<p>源码：<a href=\"https://github.com/rtic-rs\" title=\"Real-Time Interrupt-driven Concurrency (RTIC) · GitHub\">Real-Time Interrupt-driven Concurrency (RTIC) · GitHub</a></p>\n<p>基于RUST的编程代码性能并不比C差，之前跟大家分享过一个测试比较贴：<a href=\"https://www.armbbs.cn/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=111995\" title=\"网友做的Embassy/Rust 和 FreeRTOS/C的速度比较 - 编程语言 -  硬汉嵌入式论坛 -  Powered by Discuz!\">网友做的Embassy/Rust 和 FreeRTOS/C的速度比较 - 编程语言 - 硬汉嵌入式论坛 - Powered by Discuz!</a></p>\n<p>特色：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1d21d08539354bf28e65071ca73e9999.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>文档：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\dfceacb6e3e74b9481f612dbb6fedaa5.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>3、TouchGFX V4.20发布，更新大量功能</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.st.com/touchgfx/\" title=\"TouchGFX 4.20: Sharing Custom Containers Is Caring! Check the New Export Feature\">TouchGFX 4.20: Sharing Custom Containers Is Caring! Check the New Export Feature</a></p>\n<p>支持导入导出自定义容器，方便多人协作共享素材，同时提升矢量图形的性能展示，一些场景下，性能可以提升70%</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\e48fc25ef99e4e65b2a98f1e0e67603c.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>4、基于SiP封装技术设计的nRF5340模组ISP2053-AX</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.insightsip.com/products/bluetooth-smart-modules/isp2053\" title=\"https://www.insightsip.com/produ ... art-modules/isp2053\">https://www.insightsip.com/produ ... art-modules/isp2053</a></p>\n<p>nRF5340是Nordic之前推出的一款双核M33物联网芯片，通过SiP封装了天线，DC/DC。晶振等元件后，大大方便客户硬件设计。</p>\n<p>规格：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\8aa1cb59c560482b8cb972a43dabeb6b.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>框图：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\d98960a8ca4440c69c970c7557e6a5d6.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>效果：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\11cef0779b7f494e81488bfe6c7d7895.png\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ca8e2ca6d2344ff895461d4b603830dd.png\"/> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>5、AMD和亿咖通ECARX合作开发下一代电动汽车的沉浸式数字驾驶舱车载计算平台</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amd.com/en/press-releases/2022-08-04-amd-and-ecarx-to-collaborate-immersive-digital-cockpit-vehicle-computing\" title=\"https://www.amd.com/en/press-releases/2022-08-04-amd-and-ecarx-to-collaborate-immersive-digital-cockpit-vehicle-computing\">https://www.amd.com/en/press-releases/2022-08-04-amd-and-ecarx-to-collaborate-immersive-digital-cockpit-vehicle-computing</a></p>\n<p>数字驾驶舱将由 AMD 锐龙嵌入式 V2000 处理器和AMD镭龙RX6000系列GPU提供支持</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\86afd6a2ed20452f9a1d4971d4deb90e.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>6、Microchip发布的ThreadX配合硬件加密芯片ATECC608的物联网安全操作</strong></p>\n<p>文章中分享了如何通过硬件加密芯片ATECC608配合ThreadX实现物联网设备实现安全启动和 TLS 相互身份验证</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0478d6a073874706b1bb9894130a041f.png\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\33f229e6197d46cc998d7f3564203de4.png\"/> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ce6ee398a74c46c4a25e9449611e9c20.png\"/> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>7、沁恒制作的USB选型指南</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://special.wch.cn/zh_cn/USBChips/#/\" title=\"USB芯片索引-南京沁恒微电子股份有限公司\">USB芯片索引-南京沁恒微电子股份有限公司</a></p>\n<p>选型框图做的非常不错，大大方便用户查找</p>\n<p>下面的小方框可以方便的查找</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\8c5924d436ba48508de0d992ee51f810.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>8、工业物联网4.0书籍，PDF格式</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://download.armfly.com/armbbs/bbs/114755/BooKChapter-IIOTIndustry4.0.pdf\" title=\"BooKChapter-IIOTIndustry4.0.pdf\">BooKChapter-IIOTIndustry4.0.pdf</a> (7.57MB)</p>\n<p>封皮：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\6ee0a81efd41487890ff4d18354cf4ae.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>目录：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\671d54263949467daa95a9760c0829c3.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>书籍整理的知识点还不错，大家有兴趣可以看看</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\a4dd2496c1894a7880d00792635c391b.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>9、emWin新发布的两期AppWizard视频教程</strong></p>\n<p>（1）SEGGER新发布的ApppWizard 滚轮控件Wheel视频教程使用方法</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/c967d87e42804918ac14e3f33fce412b.gif\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\d2518459895e4af6b5e9fc8e99e86f3b.png\"/> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>（2）ApppWizard 多窗口滑动切换视频教程</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\9140de49143043c48f66dacafad108ae.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>10、美国的520亿美元芯片法案通过了</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.semi.org/en/news-media-press-releases/semi-press-releases/semi-applauds-president-biden%27s-signing-of-chips-and-science-act-of-2022\" title=\"https://www.semi.org/en/news-media-press-releases/semi-press-releases/semi-applauds-president-biden%27s-signing-of-chips-and-science-act-of-2022\">https://www.semi.org/en/news-media-press-releases/semi-press-releases/semi-applauds-president-biden%27s-signing-of-chips-and-science-act-of-2022</a></p>\n<p>前段时间的欧洲芯片法案目标是到2030年欧洲达到全球半导体产量的20%，这次美国的芯片法案也通过了，预示着全球芯片竞赛正式拉开序幕。</p>\n<p>政府的参与在使得本土芯片厂家收益的同时，不可避免的会整点骚套路限制其他国家，国家之间的芯片竞争的将愈演愈烈。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\edfa29aa4e61450095dd128a2b05c6e2.png\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>11、TI推出的固态继电器芯片实现更可靠的隔离</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://e2e.ti.com/blogs_/b/powerhouse/posts/how-to-achieve-higher-reliability-isolation-and-a-smaller-solution-size-with-ssrs\" title=\"How to achieve higher-reliability isolation and a smaller solution size with solid-state relays - Power management - Technical articles - TI E2E support forums\">How to achieve higher-reliability isolation and a smaller solution size with solid-state relays - Power management - Technical articles - TI E2E support forums</a></p>\n<p>固态继电器以最快的速度、最高的工作温度和最低的系统成本提供最高的介电强度。它们还可以在更小的封装中实现更可靠的开关操作</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\587df8ef563b46ff8c8dbf6862c8de5f.png\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1fdcfc3caccd4f5d90c71dea18ee22f7.png\"/> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c7433a90547842b782841d0037a8bed8.png\"/> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><br/><strong>12、H7-TOOL本周更新</strong></p>\n<p>H7-TOOL详细介绍：<a href=\"https://www.armbbs.cn/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=89934\" title=\"H7-TOOL开发工具，1拖4/16脱机烧录，高速DAPLINK仿真，CAN助手，串口助手，示波器，RTT等，支持WiFi，以太网，高速USB和手持版 - H7-TOOL开发工具 -  硬汉嵌入式论坛 -  Powered by Discuz!\">H7-TOOL开发工具，1拖4/16脱机烧录，高速DAPLINK仿真，CAN助手，串口助手，示波器，RTT等，支持WiFi，以太网，高速USB和手持版 - H7-TOOL开发工具 - 硬汉嵌入式论坛 - Powered by Discuz!</a></p>\n<p><strong>（1） H7-TOOL的LUA小程序实现JSCope HSS模式操作说明已经发布</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.armbbs.cn/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=114644\" title=\"H7-TOOL的LUA小程序实现JSCope HSS模式操作说明，已经发布（2022-08-11） - H7-TOOL开发工具 -  硬汉嵌入式论坛 -  Powered by Discuz!\">H7-TOOL的LUA小程序实现JSCope HSS模式操作说明，已经发布（2022-08-11） - H7-TOOL开发工具 - 硬汉嵌入式论坛 - Powered by Discuz!</a></p>\n<p>HSS模式的优势：全程无需复位芯片，直接读取即可。</p>\n<p>而且随时随地都可以连接目标板，不影响目标板的正常功能，不需要额外资源。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/ce00c802a16b40fd8ecc4a0f8d81af7d.gif\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>（2）H7-TOOL硬件异常黑盒子检测功能制作完成</strong></p>\n<p>首版功能差不多已经完成，这两天整理后分享</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\6795754fc3a8472a9138443d82a367ec.png\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\8d5ead13b4e14f27b0865fe031b80828.png\"/> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>（3）脑洞大开，可以基于H7-TOOL做一个支持各种RTOS的任务执行情况检测功能了</strong></p>\n<p>待本周发布了硬件异常黑盒子功能后，就开始制作这个功能</p>\n<p>采用LUA小程序实现，将各种RTOS都做个支持。</p>\n<p>像uCProbe，SystemView，ThreadX TraceX都是这种功能的代表。</p>\n<p>通过TOOL的LUA小程序优势是我们可以脱机检测而不依赖于电脑，任务栈，系统栈等都可以做个检测实现。</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "PHP", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 1, "time": "2022-08-16 17:35:53", "summary": "往期周报汇总地址：嵌入式周报硬汉嵌入式论坛嵌入式周报硬汉嵌入式论坛本周更新一期视频教程视频教程第期：运算加速的精髓，含指令，饱和运算指令和浮点以及定点的乘累加指令视频教程第期：运算加速的精髓，含指令，"}